---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Methodology - How We Review Credit Cards | ProofLabs"
  description="Learn how ProofLabs reviews and ranks credit cards using objective, data-driven analysis."
>
  <div class="container-custom" style="padding: 8rem 0 6rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text);">
        Our Methodology
      </h1>
      
      <div style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 600;">
          Every credit card review on ProofLabs is evaluated using a comprehensive, data-driven methodology designed to provide objective, actionable insights.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Evaluation Criteria
        </h2>
        
        <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text);">
            1. Rewards Rate Analysis
          </h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            We calculate effective rewards rates across different spending categories, considering bonus categories, caps, and earning restrictions. We model real-world spending patterns to determine actual value.
          </p>
          
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text);">
            2. Fee Structure Evaluation
          </h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Annual fees, foreign transaction fees, balance transfer fees, and other charges are factored into our analysis. We calculate break-even points for cards with annual fees.
          </p>
          
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text);">
            3. Sign-Up Bonus Value
          </h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            We assess welcome offers based on minimum spend requirements, time to earn, and actual cash value of points/miles using current redemption rates.
          </p>
          
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text);">
            4. Benefits & Perks
          </h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Travel credits, purchase protection, extended warranties, lounge access, and other benefits are quantified and included in overall value calculations.
          </p>
          
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text);">
            5. APR & Interest Rates
          </h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            For cards targeting balance transfers or purchases, we evaluate intro APR periods, ongoing rates, and penalty APR terms.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Ranking Process
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          Cards are scored on a 100-point scale across multiple dimensions. We calculate weighted scores based on the card's target audience and primary use case. Rankings are updated whenever card terms change or new competitive offers emerge.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Independence & Transparency
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          ProofLabs may earn affiliate commissions when readers apply for credit cards through our links. However, our reviews and rankings are determined solely by our methodology—not by commission rates or advertising relationships.
        </p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We maintain strict editorial independence. Card issuers have no input on our reviews, rankings, or methodology.
        </p>
        
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Data Sources
        </h2>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          We gather data from card issuer websites, official terms and conditions, and verified regulatory disclosures. All rates, fees, and offers are verified before publication and updated daily.
        </p>
        
        <div style="background-color: var(--color-secondary-bg); border-left: 4px solid #0284c7; padding: 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-secondary-dark);">
            Questions about our methodology? <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--color-secondary); text-decoration: underline;">Contact us</a> for more details.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
